n Fractora Treat?'),(217,68,'_lyt_0_title','field_56b4d55f7e541'),(218,68,'lyt_0_intro','<p class=\"p1\">WHAT AREAS CAN BE TREATED?</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Fractora can be used on any areas that can benefit from skin renewal. The most commonly treated areas include: lower eyelid, upper eyelid, smile lines, forehead, cheeks, mouth and neck. Face and body areas that exhibit wrinkles, discoloration or acne scarring are suitable for treatment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">HOW MANY TREATMENTS?</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Depending on your Fractora treatment regime you can expect to have between 1-6 sessions. Many conditions only require 1 session!</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">HOW QUICK ARE RESULTS?</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Visible results can be seen immediately, but typically after two weeks the most noticeable results appear. Improvements continue up to three months after treatment.</p>'),(219,68,'_lyt_0_intro','field_56b4d5677e542'),(220,68,'lyt_0_button_0_label','Sign up to learn more and receive 20% off!'),(221,68,'_lyt_0_button_0_label','field_56b4d58b7e544'),(222,68,'lyt_0_button_0_url','#locations'),(223,68,'_lyt_0_button_0_url','field_56b4d5957e545'),(224,68,'lyt_0_button','1'),(225,68,'_lyt_0_button','field_56b4d5727e543'),(228,68,'lyt_0_panel_0_title','The right formula and strength'),(229,68,'_lyt_0_panel_0_title','field_56b4d6327e548'),(232,68,'lyt_0_panel','1'),(233,68,'_lyt_0_panel','field_56b4d6087e546'),(234,68,'lyt','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"panels\";}'),(235,68,'_lyt','field_56b4d4bf7e540'),(238,68,'lyt_0_panel_1_title','Easy dosage delivery'),(239,68,'_lyt_0_panel_1_title','field_56b4d6327e548'),(244,68,'lyt_0_panel_2_title','The right inert ingredients'),(245,68,'_lyt_0_panel_2_title','field_56b4d6327e548'),(250,68,'lyt_0_panel_3_title','Offer difficult to find medications'),(251,68,'_lyt_0_panel_3_title','field_56b4d6327e548'),(254,68,'lyt_0_panel_4_title','Expertise in specialized compounding'),(255,68,'_lyt_0_panel_4_title','field_56b4d6327e548'),(256,70,'_edit_last','1'),(257